gle-minded devotion and the assurance of divine support and care in return.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>One of the verses from the Bhagavad Gita that is often related to love, particularly in the sense of devotion and surrender, is: Chapter 9, Verse 22 (9.22): \u0905\u0928\u0928\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0936\u094d\u091a\u093f\u0928\u094d\u0924\u092f\u0928\u094d\u0924\u094b \u092e\u093e\u0902 \u092f\u0947 \u091c\u0928\u093e\u0903 \u092a\u0930\u094d\u092f\u0941\u092a\u093e\u0938\u0924\u0947 | \u0924\u0947\u0937\u093e\u0902&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":194,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[29],"tags":[58],"class_list":["post-451","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gurus-saadhus-kathas-mythology-en","tag-daily-dhaarmi"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/451"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=451"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/451\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/194"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=451"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=451"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=451"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}